{"title_page": "Beire (Paredes)", "text_new": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Beire \n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = \n|region             = [[Norte Region, Portugal|Norte]]\n|metro              = [[Metropolitan Area of Porto|Porto]]\n|district           = [[Porto District|Porto]]\n|municipality       = [[Paredes, Portugal|Paredes]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|41.246|-8.319|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation          = \n|area_total         = 3.31\n|population_as_of   = 2011\n|population_total   = 2040\n|patron             = \n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = \n}}\n'''Beire''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] [[Freguesia|parish]] of the [[Municipalities of Portugal|municipality]] of [[Paredes Municipality|Paredes]]. The population in 2011 was 2,040,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 3.31&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |title=\u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds |access-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105172426/http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |archive-date=2018-11-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Parishes of Paredes}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Paredes, Portugal]]\n\n\n{{Porto-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Portuguese subdivision \n|type = parish \n|official_name      = Beire \n|image_skyline      = \n|image_caption      = \n|image_flag         =\n|image_shield       = \n|image_location     = \n|region             = [[Norte Region, Portugal|Norte]]\n|metro              = [[Metropolitan Area of Porto|Porto]]\n|district           = [[Porto District|Porto]]\n|municipality       = [[Paredes, Portugal|Paredes]]\n|coordinates        = {{coord|41.246|-8.319|type:adm1st_region:PT_dim:50000|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation          = \n|area_total         = 3.31\n|population_as_of   = 2011\n|population_total   = 2040\n|patron             = \n|area_code          = \n|postal_code        = \n|website            = \n}}\n'''Beire''' is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] [[Freguesia|parish]] of the [[Municipalities of Portugal|municipality]] of [[Paredes Municipality|Paredes]]. The population in 2011 was 2,040,<ref name=ine>[http://www.ine.pt/ngt_server/attachfileu.jsp?look_parentBoui=165404348&att_display=n&att_download=y Instituto Nacional de Estat\u00edstica (INE)], Census 2011 results according to the 2013 administrative division of Portugal</ref> in an area of 3.31&nbsp;km\u00b2.<ref name=dgt>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |title=\u00c1reas das freguesias, concelhos, distritos e pa\u00eds |access-date=2018-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181105172426/http://www.dgterritorio.pt/cartografia_e_geodesia/cartografia/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal_caop_/caop__download_/carta_administrativa_oficial_de_portugal___versao_2017__em_vigor_/ |archive-date=2018-11-05 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Parishes of Paredes}}\n\n[[Category:Parishes of Paredes, Portugal]]\n\n\n{{Porto-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "